review_blob: First time I had this a month ago o was not impressed. Perhaps it had settled in to itself. Much more integrated. Coffee is strong in aroma and taste but chili is more subtle . Glad I gave it a second chance.
beer_name: Chris Banker / Insurgente / Stone Xocoveza Mocha Stout

review_blob: Doesn't feel/taste like 5.3. In fact? Not sure I've had a barrel aged with such a low ABV. Otherwise, his draft is quite nice across all areas although the body could be maltier to capture more of the stout character.
beer_name: Finchs Second Times A Charm Barrel Aged Stout
